00:11:27.000 --> 00:11:28.840
adakah anda rasa kagum

00:11:29.520 --> 00:11:30.960
atau sedikit rasa bersalah?

00:11:32.559 --> 00:11:34.719
Awak mungkin dah lupa sekarang

00:11:35.640 --> 00:11:37.239
apa yang Li Ji ingin beritahu awak

00:11:37.599 --> 00:11:39.559
di sebalik fail-fail kes ini.

00:11:40.679 --> 00:11:42.039
Hari ini, saya ingin

00:11:42.599 --> 00:11:44.359
katakan kepadamu sekali lagi.

00:11:46.599 --> 00:11:50.479
Terdapat tiga perkara penting
dalam urusan perundangan.

00:11:50.960 --> 00:11:52.159
Pertama, bukti mestilah kukuh.

00:11:52.479 --> 00:11:53.640
Cara pepejal

00:11:53.799 --> 00:11:56.159
